{"tid":2367004,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 滷肉拌麵 配 皮強豆腐","createTime":"2021-01-15T04:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T10:40:26.000Z","uid":33359,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cea25d05d2274167f5d9a25943d0b41a03378497","tid":2367004,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bxrSFK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbxrSFK2.jpg&h=f95c4ac6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kerjkK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkerjkK4.jpg&h=8bca875c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前食過佢地既滷肉飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明係好夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知點解拌麵就反而唔多夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋可能早咗啲煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲麵拎到返公司個口感已經偏淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皮強同豆腐都普普通通<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而個汁我幾鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身以為係就咁醬油膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但食落應該係餐廳自己調味過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好香既麻油味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有啲柴魚乾增加香氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落都幾c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da1a6d1cd25ab8d9e8611e3df2af873f282c7f3","tid":2367004,"uid":8304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"過分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a89245c704d